Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:18.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}好懷念 把地震填上節奏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}你會看到一個在跳舞的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:25.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}又大又藍 高高地奏響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.89,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}地球交響樂團
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辮子是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，今天不做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,別說不知道，中國三千年前的寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚，藏在什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我們知道是你拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了也不告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚是禁忌的禍根
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,說出來的話，又會有很多人 被捲入爭鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,即使要了我這條命也絕不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你意思是不能說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,四千年前，統治這裡的宰相劉白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,及輔助他而名動天下的將軍•張賢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在年輕時失去方向而想厭世之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到了雲水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,從他身上張賢知道了 千年出現一次的青龍傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在進入深山等候了十多年後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,張賢終於拿到了龍鬚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然後把它獻給了大君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,後來因為龍鬚而發生了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚的去向也被深埋在歷史中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,近年我幸運地發現 它被當做了小孩的褲帶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是最近，又被日出之國的人 帶回自己國家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是拿走龍鬚的人的畫像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何都要從這人手中，奪回龍鬚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,出發去日本！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,連續剪髮狂人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,最近在這市鎮，連續發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕女孩的頭髮 被剪的不可思議獵奇事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們區內會認為定要儘快找出對策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,需要天下無雙兼且日本第一高手的 天道先生負責市內巡視和警備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,天下無雙，兼且日本第一高手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,千萬拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,專門剪辮子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被害人好像全是留辮子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說我是最好的餌誘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辮子，是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等你們好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,終於出來了，剪髮狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你們對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛，意外地又小又弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在商量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好像已經談好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他們逃了，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,逃得真快的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，你讓他們逃掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辮子，是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,同樣的手法竟然連用兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這次絕不會讓你們逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來，給我看看你們的臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,肉包子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼！ 我們哪裡像肉包子啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那你像什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼看也是肉包子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,難道，這些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會是豆沙包？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是肉包子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是豆沙包！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,（咖喱包） 豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,住口，住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,天津甘栗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,南京雞蛋薄燒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們當人家是什麼？ （可能是薄餅包子呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有熊貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,住口，住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,肉包子也好豆沙包也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這並不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,應該還有更重要的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你們為什麼要剪走辮子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不能說，即使你要了我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在找龍鬚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（龍鬚是什麼？ ）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是龍…龍鬚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用說了 你那條辮子是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,剪髮狂人，完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,（也可能是沙律包子呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到龍鬚的時候，亂馬好不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚究竟是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,現在怎能被拿走？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比想像中更強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡必須用計謀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,迫不得已時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在四千年前，統治本地的是 宰相劉白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,輔助他而名動天下的將軍•張賢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在年輕時失去方向而想厭世之時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到了雲水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,從他身上張賢知道了在雲海深處 千年出現一次的青龍傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在進入深山，等候了十多年後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,張賢千辛萬苦，終於拿到了龍鬚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這只是晨操而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔，亂馬，吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在激動什麼，亂馬？冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚究竟是什麼，亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是裝修工人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你上油漆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全被擋開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這下糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,滿頭都是油漆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快去洗洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快去，快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你們說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會去洗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要洗乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧•亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,走廊都是油漆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜，拿毛巾來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，那些肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，解開辮子吧，這樣子不好洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不鬆開洗的話，油漆會洗不乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬真懶惰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，大家在替你擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你解開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,別碰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的頭髮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼也不肯的話，只好硬來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你逃了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這事不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,來人，快攔住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,（給我安靜！ ）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真會麻煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小靡，好好抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,的確沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,綁這辮子的帶子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是中國四千年的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,龍鬚…是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事，亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，龍鬚究竟是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這龍鬚，是我的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,封印？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,封印？ （充公）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果解開了辮子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,會發生可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，洗個頭害我都沒時間吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，你在生什麼氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辮子的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了，這種事沒什麼好說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不好，因為你正被追擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那些肉包子，我不會這麼算數的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然已經找到龍鬚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙比想像中更麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不一定要用武力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼好辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧，過去交給我的事中 有失敗過的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說我真難開口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你已經兩次襲擊都失敗了囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得那的確是你的計畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我已經不想再飛天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,別怪我這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你們說話意外地坦白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是加了安眠藥的肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,經過的人會拿來吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他睡著時，我們把他的辮子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一刀剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不只我們兩人遲到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,遲到就是遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,發生意想不到的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,被其他人先撿起來吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是些嘴饞的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可能應該用更積極的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這是第三次失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等他一個人時襲擊他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬那傢伙，結果最重要的事 還是沒告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,解開辮子的話，就會發生可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，肚子好餓沒力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很想吃肉包子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就給你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們害得你沒早飯吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,力量應該只剩下了一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就等著你一個人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧，肉包子攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放了麻醉氣體的麻氣包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,已經無法動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辮子，我們收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬真是的，上課中究竟跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，身體不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到龍鬚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,別得寸進尺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,終於拿到龍鬚囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是龍鬚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是條繩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,振作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,難得你這次計謀很成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜，如果你武功再高一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊，的確太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們又被打飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這已經是第四次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這次比較痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，你在裡面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要進來了，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是亂馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，在的話回答我一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你…真的是亂馬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，你究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬竟然有這樣的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是當男人真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,當男人的野心完盡時…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請期待啊
